title: Does Eddie REALLY Know His Classical Music?! + Easy Trivia + Lunchbox Prank Calls Sports Memorabilia Shop!
itunes:title: Does Eddie REALLY Know His Classical Music?! + Easy Trivia + Lunchbox Prank Calls Sports Memorabilia Shop!
description:
Bobby shared a news story about a man getting into legal trouble for blaring classical music at his house...which then inevitably led to a studio challenge! Bobby bet Eddie that he couldn't name 3 of 6 classical composers and even put up some MONEY! Show members compete in another round of 'Easy Trivia'! Plus, Lunchbox tries to unload some "collectibles" on a sports memorabilia shop!
